T = int(raw_input())
for i in range(T):
    N = int(raw_input())
    l = raw_input().split()
    l1 = []
    for j in range(N):
        l1 = l1 + [int(l[j])]
    flag = 0
    k = max(l1)
    for j in range(k+1):
        if l1.count(j)>1:
            flag = 1
            break
    if flag==1:
        print "NO"
    else:
        print "YES"
